Hi there,

I got the solution. It's my fault.

The function revised to the following form, then I got the same result.

mass <- function(time, state, params) {
     with(as.list(c(state, params)), {
             H2O <- K3 * H * O
             dH <- -K1 * H2O
             dO <- -K2 * H2O
             dH2O <- H2O
             list(c(dH, dO, dH2O))
     })
}

Best,
Jinsong

